The cumulative total number that we report here (and for all days going forward unless otherwise mentioned) is from a png infographic that pops up when you click on "infographic vietnam" partway down the page. The "132,771" we extracted is the red number shown in the 2nd last gray box in a row of 5-6 gray boxes shown in the bottom third of the png.
